name: Alycia
context_summary: Fineguide, a platform that allows users to create AI chat assistants for websites without coding. The assistants offer 24/7 customer support, aid in employee onboarding, manage appointment scheduling, and enhance e-commerce sales through customer behavior analysis, featuring customizable options and predefined prompts for quick setup.
